priorities from `/Users/virginia.zambudio/PlaywrightAutomation/artifacts/outputs/quality-engineering-planning/qa-master-test-plan`. Write one Gherkin suite file per epic
plus a coverage manifest to `/Users/virginia.zambudio/PlaywrightAutomation/artifacts/outputs/quality-engineering-design/test-cases`.

Read inputs from: /Users/virginia.zambudio/PlaywrightAutomation/artifacts/outputs/product-delivery/user-stories
